" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529829\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529829\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mbq1665703005578.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mbq1665703005578.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mbq1665703005578.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mbq1665703005578\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">numset\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__numset_230095\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Initialize the value of the specified counter.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__topic_d74738e1_d74739e1_d74740e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__p_d74741e1_d74742e1_d74743e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">numset</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CounterName</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InitialValue</var> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__topic_d49232e1_d49233e1_d49234e1_d49235e1_d49236e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d647968e76\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CounterName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__3\">\n Name of a counter in <var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InitialValue</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__2\">\n Number\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__3\"> A numeric expression rounded down to an\n                        integer value <code class=\"ph codeph\">-2,147,483,648</code> through\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">2,147,483,647</code>  (that is,\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">-2<sup class=\"ph sup\">31</sup></code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">2<sup class=\"ph sup\">31</sup></code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6995e1_d6996e1_d6997e1__entry__3\">\n Name of the library to which <var class=\"keyword varname\">CounterName</var> belongs. If omitted, the library SYSTEM_LIBRARY is used.\n <p class=\"p\">Libraries allow different projects to maintain their own set of counters. (The current library is available in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span>.)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__topic_d49237e1_d49238e1_d49239e1_d49240e1_d49241e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d647968e191\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6998e1_d6999e1_d7000e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6998e1_d6999e1_d7000e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6998e1_d6999e1_d7000e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6998e1_d6999e1_d7000e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6998e1_d6999e1_d7000e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CounterName</var> was successfully initialized.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6998e1_d6999e1_d7000e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d6998e1_d6999e1_d7000e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InitialValue</var> was out of range, <var class=\"keyword varname\">CounterName</var> not defined, or Uniface was unable to access the Repository.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">numgen</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">numset</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\"> Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-12</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UIOSERR_*&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Errors during database I/O. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-30</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UNETERR_*&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Errors during network I/O. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1108</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_COUNTER&gt;\n\t\t\t\t </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Uniface was unable to access the\n\t\t\t\t Repository or the counter is not defined. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1203</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_RANGE&gt;\n\t\t\t\t </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mbq1665703005578__table_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Value out of range. The value of the\n\t\t\t\t increment or the generated counter is incorrect. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__topic_d49242e1_d49243e1_d49244e1_d49245e1_d49246e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d647968e387\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__d6482e20\">Allowed in all component types except self-contained Report and Services.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__topic_d49247e1_d49248e1_d49249e1_d49250e1_d49251e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d647968e397\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__p_d74759e1_d74760e1_d74761e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">numset</span> statement initializes <var class=\"keyword varname\">CounterName</var> to the value <var class=\"keyword varname\">InitialValue</var>. The statement can be used to initialize counters that are used by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">numgen</span> statement.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__p_d74762e1_d74763e1_d74764e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nlv1665703005447.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nlv1665703005447.html#nlv1665703005447__topic_d49212e1_d49213e1_d49214e1_d49215e1_d49216e1\">Using Counters</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__section_rqt_r3h_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d647968e425\">Example: Resetting a Counter</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example resets the counter NUMBERCOUNTER in the library\n               SALES_LIBRARY to 0:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mbq1665703005578__pre_zw2_s3h_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; trigger: Detail\n\nnumset \"NUMBERCOUNTER\", 0,\"SALES_LIBRARY\"\ncommit \"$UUU\"\nmessage \"Counter %%NUMBERCOUNTER in SALES_LIBRARY set to 0.\"\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nlv1665703005447.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>numgen</a><p>Increment the value of the specified counter.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exe1665702665391.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$variation</a><p>Return or specify the name of the library containing objects needed by the application or component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529829\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529829\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "numset Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 numset Initialize the value of the specified counter. numset CounterName , InitialValue { , LibraryName } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description CounterName String Name of a counter in LibraryName . InitialValue Number A numeric expression rounded down to an integer value -2,147,483,648 through 2,147,483,647 (that is, -2 31 through 2 31 -1 ). LibraryName String Name of the library to which CounterName belongs. If omitted, the library SYSTEM_LIBRARY is used. Libraries allow different projects to maintain their own set of counters. (The current library is available in $variation .) Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $status Value Meaning 0 CounterName was successfully initialized. -1 InitialValue was out of range, CounterName not defined, or Uniface was unable to access the Repository. Table 3. Values commonly returned by $procerror following numgen and numset Value Error constant Meaning -2 through -12 <UIOSERR_*> Errors during database I/O. -16 through -30 <UNETERR_*> Errors during network I/O. -1108 <UPROCERR_COUNTER> Uniface was unable to access the Repository or the counter is not defined. -1203 <UPROCERR_RANGE> Value out of range. The value of the increment or the generated counter is incorrect. Use Allowed in all component types except self-contained Report and Services. Description The numset statement initializes CounterName to the value InitialValue . The statement can be used to initialize counters that are used by the numgen statement. For more information, see Using Counters . Example: Resetting a Counter The following example resets the counter NUMBERCOUNTER in the library SALES_LIBRARY to 0: ; trigger: Detail numset \"NUMBERCOUNTER\", 0,\"SALES_LIBRARY\" commit \"$UUU\" message \"Counter %%NUMBERCOUNTER in SALES_LIBRARY set to 0.\" Copy Related Links numgen Increment the value of the specified counter. $variation Return or specify the name of the library containing objects needed by the application or component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}